Zero Hubbard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zero_Hubbard 0 Zero Hubbard, also known as Zerondrick Hubbard, is an American actor best known for his childhood roles in the 1980s. Zero Hubbard was born in Little Rock, Arkansas on February 22, 1971. Zero_Hubbard , also_known as Zerondrick_Hubbard , is an_American_actor best_known for his_childhood_roles in the_1980s .
